{
    "title": "Festa Imodesta",
    "artist": "Chico Buarque",
    "composer": "Caetano Veloso / Luiz Queiroga / Teresa Cristina",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C6(9)\">C6(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Numa festa imodesta como esta</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#m7\">D#m7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A5+/7\">A5+/7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Vamos homenagear</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm(7M)\">Dm(7M)</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm6\">Dm6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Todo aquele que nos empresta sua testa</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7M\">F7M</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7(b9)\">G7(b9)</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7(13)\">G7(13)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Construindo coisas pra se cantar</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C6(9)\">C6(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tudo  aquilo que o malandro pronun_cia</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">                   Gm4 (descobrir)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E que o otário silen__cia</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7/9\">C7/9</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7M\">F7M</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A#7/9\">A#7/9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Toda festa que se dá ou não se dá</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7(13)\">G7(13)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Passa pela fresta da cesta e resta a vida</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C6(9)\">C6(9)</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7(b13)\">A7(b13)</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#°\">D#°</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ah!           acima do coração</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C/E\">C/E</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que sofre com razão</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">    Dm7     G7(13)  Gm4 (descobrir)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A razão que vota no coração</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7/9\">C7/9</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7M\">F7M</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E acima da razão a rima</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A#7/9\">A#7/9</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E acima da rima a nota da canção</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7(13)\">G7(13)</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7/9\">C7/9</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7(b13)\">A7(b13)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Bemol, natural, sustenida      no ar</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#°\">D#°</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C/E\">C/E</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Viva aquele que se presta a esta ocupação</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7(13)\">G7(13)</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C6(9)\">C6(9)</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7(b13)\">A7(b13)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Salve o compositor popular</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7(13)\">G7(13)</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C6(9)\">C6(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Salve o compositor popular</span>\n",
